LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       OH_4.lmp
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (7.097 7.097 24.588)
  1 by 2 by 4 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  34 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.0110435 secs

timestep 0.25

# ---------- Define Interatomic Potential ---------------------
